summary: Small Loot Dungeon accessible under the first bridge in Whiterun
descriptionHtml:
Just a simple place I added with a bunch of loot and things to find. You can access it from under the first bridge in the entrance of Whiterun. Enter Whiterun and jump under the bridge just before the blacksmith. 

Anything that should be added/changed let me know in comments or PM. 

Sorry for the stairs, I didnt know the GenKit items had messed up stairs. you have to jump up them for some reason.
author: MastaJ96 Sparkey96 -steam
